<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I believe each reader my have a different interpretation. I&apos;m familiar with Francine River but have not read her books. Lynn Austin&apos;s books are consid<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I believe each reader my have a different interpretation. I'm familiar with Francine River but have not read her books. Lynn Austin's books are considered similar to authors Lisa Wingate and Colleen Coble. I didn't find this book to be overdone with scripture quotes but meaningful and helpful when included. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
