        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2393817733" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13135432137046276799">Wow!!! Really! This book was just amazing! Faith, courage and perseverance! LOVED Eli..: to have the faith that he had as a African American slave in the Civil War... wow! What great insight in a dreadful time of history for our country! Amazing!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


